Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.71,0:00:02.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟  乌丸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.28,0:00:06.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啦…那个什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.64,0:00:09.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fe128\fnDFMaruGothic-Md\fs27}塚{\r}本的生日晚会玩得高兴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.57,0:00:12.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漫画那边  我尽力好歹算是搞定了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.44,0:00:15.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用谢了  再见
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.79,0:00:17.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话是这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.94,0:00:20.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但还是很在意那家伙的漫画到底怎么样了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.56,0:00:22.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为只交了我画的原稿…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.69,0:00:26.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！这…这究竟是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.37,0:02:09.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然把你叫出来真是不好意思啊  妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.37,0:02:11.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.04,0:02:17.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不知为何我画的漫画竟然代替乌丸的登上去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.77,0:02:18.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.20,0:02:21.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？寒假要去台湾旅游？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.01,0:02:24.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊…我就只能住住外婆家而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.33,0:02:25.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.18,0:02:30.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这期的这个漫画  虽然画技不怎么样但还挺有趣的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.36,0:02:31.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.40,0:02:32.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！我也看了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.21,0:02:35.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是以前的四格漫画了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.45,0:02:37.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈里马哈里欧  新人？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.80,0:02:42.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯哼哼哼哼…作者大人就在你们旁边
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.55,0:02:45.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过「画技不怎么样」你这句话是多余的  周防
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.74,0:02:50.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…感觉内容很幼稚啊  这个人肯定没有恋爱经历
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.94,0:02:52.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙怎么到哪里都这样！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.78,0:02:55.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  我觉得这类还不错的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.22,0:02:58.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太复杂的看起来比较头痛啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.32,0:03:01.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯  周防  你是个好人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.32,0:03:04.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后给你签个名好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.54,0:03:09.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？但是  突然男女主角就同居了这不现实嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.13,0:03:13.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为就算是漫画也不能想怎么画就怎么画哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.57,0:03:16.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的看着看着就不爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.68,0:03:21.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐  你真是个内心已完全枯涸的可悲女人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.19,0:03:25.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对你的感觉已经超越了可恨  达到了可悲的境界了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.49,0:03:27.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天满你觉得怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.03,0:03:30.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔！说得好！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.98,0:03:33.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高野  我给你两张签名！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.11,0:03:35.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.70,0:03:36.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.99,0:03:39.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我已经准备好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.91,0:03:43.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧  让我听一听  你的内心想法！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.26,0:03:46.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.88,0:03:48.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.41,0:03:50.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓漫画  就是它里面充满着梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.25,0:03:53.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会让人觉得发生这样的事也不错哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.80,0:03:58.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功啦！不枉作为作者的我的劳动啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.08,0:04:02.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如你所说的啊  我果然没搞错啊  小满
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.66,0:04:10.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.06,0:04:13.08,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（谈讲社  不存在实际的此楼模型）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.08,0:04:14.36,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（ZINEGAMA编辑部）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.33,0:04:14.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.60,0:04:16.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀～真是很有趣啊  田泽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.00,0:04:19.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}读者的评价也很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.41,0:04:23.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那我就要再努力用漫画让小满更加高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.49,0:04:23.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}从漫画里能看出一目了然的心思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.22,0:04:27.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？后面那位是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.98,0:04:30.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我是助手{\fe128\fnDFMaruGothic-Md\fs27}塚{\r}本
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.65,0:04:34.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为她也帮助我一起完成原稿  所以就带她过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.68,0:04:35.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.61,0:04:52.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.93,0:04:54.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  总编辑  他就是田泽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.05,0:04:57.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…我…那个…我是哈里…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.97,0:05:00.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.42,0:05:03.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…喂  别…别过去啊  妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.91,0:05:10.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…总编辑的工作就是吓唬新人漫画家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.39,0:05:14.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子胡说八道些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.67,0:05:15.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会被杀的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.67,0:05:26.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到我寸步没有退缩的  你是第一人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.82,0:05:28.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多多指教了  小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.98,0:05:30.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.46,0:05:33.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总编辑二十年未曾出现的笑容啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.58,0:05:34.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  三十年了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.57,0:05:54.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您确实和鬼哭丸船长是旧相识…是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.74,0:05:56.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.41,0:06:01.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我在那艘船上  从船长那里得到了这支笔…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.70,0:06:04.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下个星期之前给我画好120张的漫画来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.74,0:06:16.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完蛋了完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.24,0:06:17.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然要画120张
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.78,0:06:18.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.92,0:06:20.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寒假不用去学校
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.35,0:06:22.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道只能窝在房间里拼命画了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.84,0:06:24.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  弦子  我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.91,0:06:27.97,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（我和叶子要去滑雪旅行一段时间  还要泡温泉哦  一周后回来  好自为之  零花钱  弦子借给你的  加油哦拳儿）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.64,0:06:33.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切…算了  安静点我还好工作  也倒不错…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.90,0:06:35.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,门上锁了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.01,0:06:38.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.22,0:06:40.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…播磨学长…钥匙呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.01,0:06:41.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没带
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.18,0:06:42.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.47,0:06:50.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  姐姐  寒假这段时间暂且收留他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.65,0:06:54.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让播磨学长寄宿在我们家里吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.01,0:06:58.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊——！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.63,0:07:04.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  姐姐  寒假这段时间暂且收留他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.79,0:07:07.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让播磨学长寄宿在我们家里吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.79,0:07:07.02,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（被抛弃的狗）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.15,0:07:07.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汪！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.55,0:07:10.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊——！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.31,0:07:13.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊……
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.36,0:07:16.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做  做了个诡异的梦啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.55,0:07:20.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然就住到小满家里去了  这也想得太美了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.01,0:07:23.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话又说回来  这个梦是从哪里开始的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.41,0:07:25.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是弦子的旅行？还是总编辑？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.37,0:07:28.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫…莫非是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.70,0:07:30.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从ZINEGAMA登上我的漫画开始？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.61,0:07:35.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  哎  哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.24,0:07:38.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是…做梦吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.32,0:07:40.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,播磨  起来了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.17,0:07:44.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是做梦啊～～～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.60,0:07:48.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,播磨学长  饭这些够了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.46,0:07:53.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八云做的味噌汤可是一绝哦  播磨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.79,0:07:55.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是个幸福的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.16,0:07:59.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我开动啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.73,0:08:01.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别客气  尽管吃哦  播磨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.27,0:08:03.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.90,0:08:10.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛…果然不是梦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.51,0:08:13.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和…和小满同住一个屋檐下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.26,0:08:15.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还同坐在一个被炉里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.80,0:08:19.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…酱油…酱油…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.17,0:08:23.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给  这个是酱油  墨鱼形状的瓶子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.59,0:08:27.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,播磨  有什么不明白的尽管问我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.99,0:08:33.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一大清早就让我这么幸福真的可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.11,0:08:36.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然职业漫画家就是不一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.22,0:08:41.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.10,0:08:42.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.32,0:08:46.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么把那几个盘子放到碗柜的最上面好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.08,0:08:48.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.02,0:08:50.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放…放这里行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.04,0:08:52.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.74,0:08:55.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是男孩子  处理高的地方就是小菜一碟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.73,0:08:59.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  这点算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.83,0:09:03.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶！这不就和新婚夫妇一样了吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.92,0:09:09.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小满  从今天  从现在开始  我就是你的仆人了～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.69,0:09:12.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？播磨学长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.53,0:09:17.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…妹妹  接下去要洗衣服吗  交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.48,0:09:20.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…那个…播磨学长还是先去忙原稿吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.48,0:09:25.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原稿吧  原稿吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.72,0:09:28.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘得一干二净了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.72,0:09:33.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原稿还要画120张啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.25,0:09:43.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,处于成长期的空太现在已经长到了3米
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.71,0:09:46.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇！好厉害  长得太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.61,0:09:48.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…好大哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.20,0:09:50.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？怎么了播磨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.13,0:09:53.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个  我有些口渴了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.70,0:09:55.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  抱歉抱歉  我没注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.13,0:09:58.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了  告诉我地方我自己去好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.28,0:10:01.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么呢  你可是重要的客人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.12,0:10:03.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖啡可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.68,0:10:04.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.54,0:10:09.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要再来一杯的话就说哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.56,0:10:11.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.92,0:10:15.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油哦  播磨  虽然不知道你在干什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.47,0:10:20.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  昨天你带播磨回来的时候我还真吓了一大跳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.03,0:10:22.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思啊  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.12,0:10:24.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.93,0:10:27.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为八云你很少请求我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.89,0:10:29.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这次就不管任何理由啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.08,0:10:31.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才像姐姐的样子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.10,0:10:36.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.10,0:10:41.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.65,0:10:46.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…播磨他真的不要吃午饭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.21,0:10:49.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  他说他现在要集中精力工作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.19,0:10:51.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  集中精力啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.25,0:10:53.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知道他在做什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.37,0:10:59.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,播磨他连点心也不要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.16,0:11:01.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我稍微去看看他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.93,0:11:03.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油吧  年轻的太太！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.53,0:11:05.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是那样的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.37,0:11:12.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过真是不可思议啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.13,0:11:14.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧  伊织
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.29,0:11:20.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,播磨学长  那个…我进来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.93,0:11:23.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原稿的进度怎么样了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.53,0:11:29.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.90,0:11:35.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…不介意的话  稍微休息一下吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.47,0:11:36.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.91,0:11:38.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,画不出好漫画！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.40,0:11:41.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是…决定好画什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.77,0:11:44.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但实在是不知道怎么构图
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.49,0:11:47.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…如果我可以的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.99,0:11:48.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来帮你摆动作吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.73,0:11:51.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗  妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.92,0:11:52.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.30,0:11:59.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实空太每天都会长10公分哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.60,0:12:01.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长太快了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.84,0:12:06.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该准备晚饭了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.73,0:12:11.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我现在好不容易能帮上播磨学长了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.64,0:12:13.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就再等一会儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.25,0:12:20.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说空太今天吃了77篮的饲料
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.83,0:12:22.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多吃点长得越来越…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.62,0:12:24.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还要吃更多哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.47,0:12:26.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…什么玩意儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.82,0:12:30.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢啦  妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.64,0:12:32.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  糟糕  墨水用完了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.04,0:12:35.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…我去买吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.45,0:12:36.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能总是麻烦你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.37,0:12:39.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  正好顺路的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.69,0:12:42.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是吗  那拜托啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.54,0:12:43.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.14,0:12:48.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我肚子饿了啊～八云～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.53,0:12:51.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八云  现在出去买东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.86,0:12:55.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起姐姐  晚饭的准备有些迟了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.83,0:12:57.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦  没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.44,0:12:59.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新婚就要吃亲手做的料理呢～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.71,0:13:00.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好恩爱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.01,0:13:02.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…说了不是那回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.51,0:13:06.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.31,0:13:11.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天好冷啊  已经是严冬了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.11,0:13:17.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了  回来得真是太晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.95,0:13:19.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧  真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.99,0:13:24.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,播磨你真搞笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.65,0:13:26.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  就这么下去做我们家的家人吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.96,0:13:28.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.44,0:13:29.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是作为弟弟哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.82,0:13:31.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.49,0:13:33.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先把话说在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.36,0:13:36.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电视频道调换顺序是我  八云  拳儿哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.45,0:13:38.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拳儿…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.76,0:13:40.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.58,0:13:42.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑容…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.26,0:13:45.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八云你回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.15,0:13:47.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么那么～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.41,0:13:49.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电灯泡就离开啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.83,0:13:51.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.73,0:13:53.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…虽然不知道在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.56,0:13:57.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…播磨学长  墨水买来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.56,0:13:59.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你啊  妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.03,0:14:01.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不客气…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.26,0:14:06.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹妹  我浑身充满干劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.84,0:14:11.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么！一口气画它个120页！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.82,0:14:17.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.22,0:14:21.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您下定决心了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.30,0:14:23.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用什么决心不决心的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.98,0:14:26.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家里说的话是没办法反抗的不是么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.94,0:14:28.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且妈妈好像也有那个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.30,0:14:34.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我不在了  也不会有谁在意的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.38,0:14:45.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绵薄之力也好  想帮上播磨学长的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.26,0:14:49.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊织  怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.52,0:14:51.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传单？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.63,0:14:56.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漫画编辑学校…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.11,0:15:00.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢各位今日出席我们的讲座
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.72,0:15:00.67,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（谈讲社  不存在实际的此楼模型）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.13,0:15:02.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.60,0:15:04.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我来介绍一下今天的讲师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.13,0:15:06.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是渔夫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.56,0:15:10.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是负责周刊少年ZINEGAMAN事务的五岛总编辑！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.26,0:15:20.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论何时何地都要让他画漫画
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.51,0:15:22.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是住院或者是失恋也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.63,0:15:34.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.92,0:15:39.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样？毕业以后要不要来我们的编辑部呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.78,0:15:45.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到了这个东西…资格认定徽章
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.99,0:15:48.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是讲课的内容还是不太清楚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.14,0:15:56.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的～看到八云和播磨两个人恩恩爱爱的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.31,0:15:57.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连我这个做姐姐的都心跳不已呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.24,0:16:00.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～恋爱真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.44,0:16:04.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来测试一下看看播磨的好男人度吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.95,0:16:07.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是姐姐的义务  也是我的权利！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.27,0:16:11.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先  我一个人是不懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.14,0:16:13.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要问问大家好男人所需具备的条件
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.24,0:16:15.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  发送
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.99,0:16:20.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方是我的话  播磨不会说实话的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.37,0:16:23.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变装变装
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.30,0:16:26.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢  那么快就回信了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.23,0:16:30.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个接着一个啊  大家还真是热情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.36,0:16:34.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,播磨学长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.73,0:16:35.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.94,0:16:39.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  那个…不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.91,0:16:42.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  真完美
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.75,0:16:46.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊织  伊织
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.48,0:16:50.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fe128\fnDFMaruGothic-Md\fs27}塚{\r}本  你到底在干什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.52,0:16:51.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.66,0:16:53.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是八云啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.45,0:16:55.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.04,0:16:58.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先从爱理回的消息开始
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.37,0:17:04.19,tiaofu-l,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-90\pos(15,245)\fad(400,400)}模仿中。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.37,0:17:04.19,tiaofu-r,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-90\pos(625,245)\fad(400,400)}{\fn@ふみゴシック\fe128}塚{\fn@文鼎特粗黑简\fe134}本天满、
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.83,0:17:03.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能察觉女孩子细微变化的男人是会被淘汰的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.75,0:17:05.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.00,0:17:07.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,播磨！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.06,0:17:11.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,播磨学长  我能问你一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.94,0:17:13.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  可以  不知道你要问什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.22,0:17:16.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有觉得今天的我和平时不同啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.78,0:17:19.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？啊…明显不同啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.39,0:17:21.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那头发和衣服怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.94,0:17:24.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一关  CLEAR
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.01,0:17:26.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.28,0:17:35.09,tiaofu-r,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-90\pos(625,245)\fad(400,400)}{\fn@ふみゴシック\fe128}塚{\fn@文鼎特粗黑简\fe134}本天满、
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.28,0:17:35.09,tiaofu-l,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-90\pos(15,245)\fad(400,400)}模仿中。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.46,0:17:32.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己做的东西无论什么都吃得很香的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.24,0:17:34.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肩膀都酸了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.42,0:17:37.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊  小美琴  同感！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.45,0:17:38.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肩膀…很酸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.06,0:17:40.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  在八云的咖喱里面…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.81,0:17:46.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放超～多的辣椒和胡椒粉  能够承受吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.41,0:17:48.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  播磨学长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.28,0:17:50.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.43,0:17:53.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小满亲手做的料理？！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.23,0:17:54.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有点痛苦但我好高兴啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.80,0:17:59.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好辣…不过挺好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.05,0:18:06.61,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,0)}（不怕辣）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.89,0:18:06.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丝毫不畏惧辛辣并且还说好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.17,0:18:08.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且吃得精光
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.50,0:18:10.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二关也  CLEAR
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.49,0:18:11.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.81,0:18:20.90,tiaofu-r,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-90\pos(625,245)\fad(400,400)}{\fn@ふみゴシック\fe128}塚{\fn@文鼎特粗黑简\fe134}本天满、
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.81,0:18:20.90,tiaofu-l,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-90\pos(15,245)\fad(400,400)}模仿中。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.91,0:18:15.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？突突突然这么问我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.73,0:18:19.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…我还是觉得能在危机时刻救我的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.56,0:18:20.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…最好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.60,0:18:23.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…真意外啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.62,0:18:26.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…危机时刻吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.81,0:18:29.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但…但是小满她为什么突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.83,0:18:31.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.96,0:18:34.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来最近我一直忙于工作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.29,0:18:36.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而总是和妹妹说话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.71,0:18:38.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才扮成妹妹的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.30,0:18:40.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而来引起我的注意吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.02,0:18:43.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  实在是太可爱了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.00,0:18:48.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让我全心全意地接受你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.33,0:18:50.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～播磨学长！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.40,0:18:53.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了！怎么啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.00,0:18:56.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有蟑螂啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.40,0:18:58.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.01,0:19:04.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我不能打它啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.09,0:19:06.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.49,0:19:08.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,播磨难道会在此处失去资格？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.65,0:19:11.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小可怜的消息还有下文啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.69,0:19:18.70,tiaofu-r,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-90\pos(625,245)}{\fn@ふみゴシック\fe128}塚{\fn@文鼎特粗黑简\fe134}本天满、
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.69,0:19:18.70,tiaofu-l,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-90\pos(15,245)}模仿中。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.94,0:19:12.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.08,0:19:15.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都用武力来解决的人就有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.04,0:19:18.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强而有力同时兼备温柔体贴的一面的人最好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.70,0:19:20.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大！逆！转！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.80,0:19:23.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三关也  CLEAR！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.71,0:19:25.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着第四关是…嵯峨野！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.66,0:19:29.03,tiaofu-r,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-90\pos(625,245)\fad(0,400)}{\fn@ふみゴシック\fe128}塚{\fn@文鼎特粗黑简\fe134}本天满、
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.66,0:19:29.03,tiaofu-l,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-90\pos(15,245)\fad(0,400)}模仿中。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.64,0:19:28.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人只要帅  完毕～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.27,0:19:32.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,播磨学长～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.42,0:19:34.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.84,0:19:35.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墨镜借用一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.15,0:19:36.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.91,0:19:38.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀…出乎意外呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.56,0:19:40.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.24,0:19:44.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这张脸好像在哪里看见过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.51,0:19:45.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.13,0:19:46.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～再给我看看嘛～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.76,0:19:48.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱…抱歉啊  太耀眼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.58,0:19:53.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千钧一发啊  没想到她居然还记得
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.84,0:19:56.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  带着墨镜就没关系了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.09,0:19:58.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合格
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.87,0:20:00.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后是小晶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.54,0:20:02.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.37,0:20:05.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,播磨学长  借点钱给我～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.15,0:20:06.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.30,0:20:08.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.20,0:20:10.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,12日元！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.42,0:20:15.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比我有钱…合格…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.57,0:20:16.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太出色了  播磨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.46,0:20:19.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是在等你这样的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.86,0:20:22.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  那…那就和我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.93,0:20:25.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和八云真是绝配啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.10,0:20:26.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.71,0:20:30.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐我也非常满意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.94,0:20:33.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  你们交往要把握分寸哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.83,0:20:37.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.00,0:20:38.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.16,0:20:40.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟  你真是个幸福的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.54,0:20:45.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然  小满还是误以为我是在和妹妹交往…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.69,0:20:49.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！必须说个清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.74,0:20:52.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再这样下去的话  我们两个一生都无法联结在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.29,0:20:56.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚  要向小满袒露一切！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.23,0:21:08.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  那个发型
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.76,0:21:12.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不好意思这个时间来打扰你  {\fe128\fnDFMaruGothic-Md\fs27}塚{\r}本
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.34,0:21:17.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本想早些这样做的  但是我一直没有勇气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.48,0:21:20.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  今晚我不会逃避了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.79,0:21:25.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…一直都很喜欢…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.25,0:21:30.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊…伊织？！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.00,0:21:33.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说  这房间是妹妹的…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.88,0:22:08.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊——！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.56,0:22:14.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空太今天又吃了好多  长得更大了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.92,0:23:47.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禁止你接近八云！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.86,0:23:50.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  School Rumble  2学期
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.96,0:23:52.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想被任何人束缚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.60,0:23:54.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想回学校也不想回家
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.68,0:23:56.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在暗夜的垂帘之中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.65,0:23:59.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,播磨  你又变成一只色猴子了啊
